data.text:

” “, maiden name in ( ) when it was shown on the card, husband was within [ ], or age within [ ], or other helpful information within [ ].

Note that some of the 3 x 5 cards were written in black felt tip marker with many letters spaced very close together. Letters such as a, c, e, i, l, o, n, r, u, were not always clear so the spelling of names may or may not be fully accurate.

Additional names and years will be added as time permits.
